gkrellflynn is a tiny system load meter for gkrellm featuring Flynn (Doomguy)

Flynn is a guy who suffers from your activity, i.e.
the applications consuming precious processor time.
Hurt him plenty!

To make Flynn smile, just click onto his face.
The DOOM graphics are the property of ID Software.

Flynn? http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doomguy

How to start it?
right click on gkrellm (or left click + F1)
go to Configuration > Plugins and enable Flynn
You may need to restart gkrellm or log out/in
